title: get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
description: Currently, the getcolumnlabel method in the meta data object is not returning user recognizable strings. This is causing confusion for end users as they need to be able to see the labels before extracting data. The expected behavior is for the getcolumnlabel method to return the same labels as displayed after extraction.
EB: The getcolumnlabel method in the meta data object is not returning user recognizable strings. The labels displayed before extraction and after extraction should be the same.
